5 Just purchased a couch and reclaimed wood cabinet, as well as, a beautiful solid wood side table at a discounted price of $72. We purchased the floor model at 1/2 the cost and the cabinet was as is. Very happy with the quality of all the pieces, the fantastic deal that we got, and the delivery being no hassle with very professional movers. The store is very well set up, no overbearing sales people trying to get their commission. Just very professional, very courteous staff to help us. This is one furniture store that has great quality merchandise (no resonated wood) all solid well built furniture at reasonable cost. We are very happy with our experience with Living Spaces and will surely recommend and come back again.
